- `docusaurus.config.ts` ‚Äî enable `it` locale, add locale dropdown
- `i18n/it/code.json` ‚Äî homepage + component strings (new)
- `i18n/it/docusaurus-theme-classic/navbar.json` ‚Äî navbar labels (new, generated)
- `i18n/it/docusaurus-theme-classic/footer.json` ‚Äî footer labels (new, generated)
- `i18n/it/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current.json` ‚Äî sidebar labels (new, generated)
- `i18n/it/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/**/*.md[x]` ‚Äî 59 translated docs (new)

## Verification

1. `yarn build` exits 0, `build/it/` exists
2. Open `build/it/index.html` ‚Äî Italian hero text visible
3. Spot-check `build/it/docs/administrator-manual/` ‚Äî Italian prose, intact code blocks
4. No broken links (Docusaurus link checker runs in build)
